HEADWORD: Blessedly
<hw>Bless"ed*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Happily; fortunately;
joyfully.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We shall <qex>blessedly</qex> meet again never to depart.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir P. Sidney.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blessedness</ent>⟦br⟧
